coins.mdf
Class TreatSwitch

java.lang.Object
  coins.mdf.TreatNode
      coins.mdf.TreatSwitch
class TreatSwitch
extends TreatNode

This class treats `SWITCH statement'. In MDF module, the `SWITCH statement' is a kind of special statement because it include the flow information.
